 #===============================================================================================================
# Soilsiu's Late Mapping Filter - for Path of Exile 2
#===============================================================================================================
# VERSION:  0.3.0
# TYPE:     Late Mapping
# AUTHOR:   Soilsiu
# 
# -> Following Allie's Guide - https://mobalytics.gg/poe-2/profile/allie/builds/0-3-allie-s-hollow-palm-invoker-starter
#
#------------------------------------
# What to Know:
#------------------------------------
# - Being a Soilsiu filter means Green is gonna be showing as GG Items or Key items
# - Smaller Font
#
# - Late Late Mapping filter is when you need to not see as many things
#  - For example this filter will hide all skill gems below 18
#  - This filter will Hide support gems 2 and below but show 3
# - Life and Mana Flasks only show if they have Quality
# - Only T14 Maps and higher show in  this Filter
#
#------------------------------------
# INSTALLATION:
#------------------------------------
#
# 1) Paste this file into the following folder: %userprofile%/Documents/My Games/Path of Exile
# 2) INGAME: Escape -> Options -> UI -> Scroll down -> Select the filter from the Dropdown box
# 
#===============================================================================================================
# Filter Settings
#===============================================================================================================

